## C5. Communicate clearly and appropriately using APA 7th referencing. (10%)

### HD
Produces work of outstanding academic quality, including exemplary structure, correct grammar, and correct APA referencing.

### D
Produces work of high academic quality, including appropriate structure, grammar, and correct APA referencing.

### C
Produces work of sound academic quality, including appropriate structure, grammar, and APA referencing.

### P
Produces work of satisfactory academic quality, including appropriate structure, grammar, and APA referencing.

### F
Does not produce work of satisfactory academic quality, including inappropriate structure, incorrect grammar, and incorrect APA referencing.
